// CHECK-NEXT:    [[TMP11:%.*]] = tail call <8 x i16> @llvm.riscv.esp.srcmb.s16.qacc.m(<16 x i8> [[TMP4]], <16 x i8> [[TMP5]], <16 x i8> [[TMP9]], <16 x i8> [[TMP10]], i32 [[SHIFT_AMOUNT]], i32 1)
